+/**
+ * Github Milestone.
+ *
+ * <p>Use a supplementary "smart" decorator to get other properties
+ * from an milestone, for example:
+ *
+ * <pre> Milestone.Smart milestone = new Milestone.Smart(origin);
+ * if (milestone.isOpen()) {
+ *   milestone.close();
+ * }</pre>
